Description: Sets the map to start the server with. If "Custom" is selected, Custom Initial Map must also be specified
Sets a custom map to use for the Initial Map, if "Custom" is selected
Sets the name of the mod directory to load, allowing the use of third-party Sven Co-op mods. Don't change this from the default 'svencoop' unless you know what you are doing!
If set, Valve Anti-Cheat (VAC) will be disabled

DisplayName: Show Spectator Talk To All Players

Description: Specifies additional [command line parameters](https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Command_line_options#Command-Line_Parameters_6) (anything that begins with a -) that are not otherwise set by AMP. Use with care

Specifies additional [console variables](https://wiki.svencoop.com/Console/Variables) (anything that begins with a +) that are not otherwise set by AMP. Use with care. Preferably, specify the equivalent under "Additional Server Settings"
Specifies additional settings to include in "server.cfg" that are not otherwise set by AMP. One setting per line

If set, support for Half Life: Opposing Force will be installed when the server is updated. This is required for some maps to work correctly. You must own Half Life: Opposing Force on Steam for this to work
If set, support for Half Life: Blue Shift will be installed when the server is updated. This is required for some maps to work correctly. You must own Half Life: Blue Shift on Steam for this to work
